{"type": "article", "id": 14415, "title": "spellworks日用系列", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-04T07:39:09Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 9, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000317ECVuKqPmR0FT6Wv4.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t日本时尚品牌 Francfranc 联合斯洛文尼亚出生的女设计师 Nika Zupanc ，推出了这套非常女性化的日用品。5 种不同颜色的餐具走着统一的可爱风，大小型号的盘子都带着波纹，水壶与茶杯都带有蝴蝶结的盖子，类似于米老鼠的耳朵，灯饰和沙发也延续了这种风格。总之很像学生时代送给女生的礼物。<a href=\"http://www.francfranc.com/issue/1505_01/?mid-bnr\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141953Z0gmCtorqEFJ3pNe.jpg\" width=\"958\" height=\"805\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.84029228\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141953DeyLnRwPWTlgK9Is.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"581\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.53796296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141954548rciCJkQwjsxuA.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"832\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.38666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}